{
  "an8.53:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 ",
  "an8.53:0.2": "6. Gotamīvagga ",
  "an8.53:0.3": "53. Saṅkhittasutta ",
  "an8.53:1.1": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ. ",
  "an8.53:1.2": "Atha kho mahāpajāpatī gotamī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā mahāpajāpatī gotamī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
  "an8.53:2.1": "“Sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā ekā vūpakaṭṭhā appamattā ātāpinī pahitattā vihareyyan”ti. ",
  "an8.53:2.2": "“Ye kho tvaṃ, gotami, dhamme jāneyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:2.3": "‘ime dhammā sarāgāya saṃvattanti, no virāgāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.4": "saṃyogāya saṃvattanti, no visaṃyogāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.5": "ācayāya saṃvattanti, no apacayāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.6": "mahicchatāya saṃvattanti, no appicchatāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.7": "asantuṭṭhiyā saṃvattanti, no santuṭṭhiyā; ",
  "an8.53:2.8": "saṅgaṇikāya saṃvattanti, no pavivekāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.9": "kosajjāya saṃvattanti, no vīriyārambhāya; ",
  "an8.53:2.10": "dubbharatāya saṃvattanti, no subharatāyā’ti, ",
  "an8.53:2.11": "ekaṃsena, gotami, dhāreyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:2.12": "‘neso dhammo, neso vinayo, netaṃ satthusāsanan’ti. ",
  "an8.53:3.1": "Ye ca kho tvaṃ, gotami, dhamme jāneyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:3.2": "‘ime dhammā virāgāya saṃvattanti, no sarāgāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.3": "visaṃyogāya saṃvattanti, no saṃyogāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.4": "apacayāya saṃvattanti, no ācayāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.5": "appicchatāya saṃvattanti, no mahicchatāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.6": "santuṭṭhiyā saṃvattanti, no asantuṭṭhiyā; ",
  "an8.53:3.7": "pavivekāya saṃvattanti, no saṅgaṇikāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.8": "vīriyārambhāya saṃvattanti, no kosajjāya; ",
  "an8.53:3.9": "subharatāya saṃvattanti, no dubbharatāyā’ti, ",
  "an8.53:3.10": "ekaṃsena, gotami, dhāreyyāsi: ",
  "an8.53:3.11": "‘eso dhammo, eso vinayo, etaṃ satthusāsanan’”ti. ",
  "an8.53:3.12": "Tatiyaṃ. "
}